## 2. API Documentation

### A. Authentication & Users (`/api/auth/`)
All endpoints are relative to your API base url (e.g. `http://localhost:8000`).

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description | Payload / Response |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **POST** | `/api/auth/register/` | None | Register a student or mentor | `{"username", "email", "password", "password_confirm", "role"}` |
| **POST** | `/api/auth/login/` | None | Login user & issue HTTPOnly refresh cookies | `{"email", "password"}` ➔ Returns `{"access", "user"}` |
| **POST** | `/api/auth/logout/` | JWT | Invalidate active refresh cookie | Standard logout |
| **POST** | `/api/auth/refresh/` | Cookie | Rotate access tokens dynamically | Reads Cookie ➔ Returns `{"access"}` |
| **GET** | `/api/auth/profile/` | JWT | Fetch logged-in user profile details | Returns user profile object |
| **POST** | `/api/auth/complete-profile/` | JWT | Set DOB, location, resume, etc. | Custom profile details |

---

### B. Landing Page (`/api/landing/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description | Response JSON structure |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **GET** | `/api/landing/` | None | Fetch site summary stats, courses, mentors, and ratings | `{"courses": [...], "mentors": [...], "stats": {...}, "reviews": [...]}` |

---

### C. Courses & Curriculum (`/api/courses/`, `/api/modules/`, `/api/lessons/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description | Path Params / Query Params |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **GET** | `/api/courses/` | JWT | List published & approved courses | Optional `?q=searchterm` |
| **GET** | `/api/courses/search/` | JWT | Elasticsearch ORM search fallback query | `?search=query` |
| **POST** | `/api/courses/` | Mentor | Create a new draft course | `{"title", "description", "price", "level", "category"}` |
| **GET** | `/api/courses/{id}/` | JWT | Retrieve course structure (modules + lesson indexes) | `{id}` |
| **POST** | `/api/courses/{id}/submit_for_review/` | Mentor | Submit course draft to moderation queue | `{id}` |
| **POST** | `/api/courses/{id}/approve/` | Admin | Approve course for catalog display | `{id}` |
| **POST** | `/api/courses/{id}/publish/` | Mentor | Publish approved course draft | `{id}` |
| **POST** | `/api/modules/` | Mentor | Add modular chapter to a course | `{"course_id", "title", "order"}` |
| **POST** | `/api/lessons/` | Mentor | Upload PDF / Video / text lecture to module | `{"module_id", "title", "content_type", ...}` |

---

### D. Reviews & Reports (`/api/reviews/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description | Payload / Response |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **GET**| `/api/courses/{course_id}/reviews/` | JWT | List all flagged-safe reviews of a course | Distribution, avg, and list of reviews |
| **POST**| `/api/courses/{course_id}/reviews/` | JWT | Submit or update review comment & rating | `{"rating": 1-5, "comment": "string"}` |
| **POST**| `/api/reviews/{id}/report/` | JWT | Flag review for administrator moderation | `{"reason": "string"}` |

---

### E. Assessment Engine (`/api/quiz-attempts/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description | Query / Response Payload |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **POST** | `/api/quiz-attempts/lessons/{lesson_id}/start/` | Student | Initiate a timed quiz attempt | Start attempts state & quiz questions list |
| **POST** | `/api/quiz-attempts/{attempt_id}/submit/` | Student | Grade answers and calculate final score | `{"answers": [{"question_id", "selected_options": [id]}]}` |
| **GET** | `/api/quiz-attempts/lessons/{lesson_id}/history/` | Student | Fetch past scores for this quiz | List of past scores |

---

### F. Payments & Checkouts (`/api/payments/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description | Payload / Response |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **POST** | `/api/payments/checkout/create-session/` | Student | Generate Stripe checkout redirect session | `{"course_id"}` ➔ Returns `{"session_url"}` |
| **POST** | `/api/payments/checkout/paypal-order/` | Student | Setup Paypal checkout execution payload | `{"course_id"}` ➔ Order details |

---

### G. Chat, Alerts & Announcements (`/api/chat/`, `/api/notifications/`, `/api/announcements/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Auth | Description | Path Params / Query Params |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **GET** | `/api/chat/rooms/` | JWT | Fetch active direct message chatrooms | List of rooms |
| **GET** | `/api/notifications/` | JWT | Retrieve user alert notifications | List of notifications |
| **POST**| `/api/notifications/{id}/read/` | JWT | Mark specific alert as read | `{id}` |
| **GET** | `/api/announcements/` | JWT | Fetch general system/enrolled course bulletins | List of bulletins |
